    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Beauty in the Broken Glass",
        "Description": "Falling in love with your own reflection is an impressive feat.\r\rThe world around you fades away from you, and you can&apos;t stop staring at your reflection. Your reflection graces the floor, mimicking the moves of the dreams you once lived.\r\rBut with the mirror&apos;s shards shattering, the crushing reality gets ahold on you. Being so self-centered, surrounded by others who can&apos;t fathom why you love yourself. Yet... You can&apos;t look away.\r\rYou can find the beauty in the broken.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as magicdave94 & Ashley.",
